# Steps to install SASS

1. Installed nvm to manage Node.js versions:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exited and reopened terminal.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16:
   nvm install 20.16
   nvm use 20.16

4. Installed SASS version 3.7.4:
   npm install sass@3.7.4

5. Verified installation:
   sass --version
